{
  "text": "where M 1 and M 2 are the molecular masses of DCBNT and solvent, respectively; m 1 and m 2 represent the corresponding mass of DCBNT and solvent, respectively. The calculation method for the mole fraction solubility (x) of DCBNT in binary solvents is the same as that of DBNT in pure solvent [CITATION_1] .",
